text: Maja Siegenthaler (born 11 November 1992) is a Swiss competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Switzerland Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
